sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant CLI as WorkspaceShow
    participant Service as WorkspaceService
    participant FS as Filesystem

    User->>CLI: workspace:show name
    CLI->>Service: getWorkspaceInfo(name)
    Service->>FS: check workspace path
    Service->>FS: scan for symlinks
    Service->>FS: check .code-workspace exists
    Service->>FS: check CLAUDE.md exists
    Service-->>CLI: workspace info
    alt not exists
        CLI-->>User: error output
    else exists
        CLI-->>User: workspace details
    end
